lead_paragraph: After suffering two setbacks in the space of a week, Atletico Madrid will be looking to avoid a third when they travel to La Liga leaders Barcelona for Saturday's top-of-the-table clash at the Nou Camp.

headline.print_headline: Atletico Anxious to Rediscover Scoring Touch at Barca
